{"id":249217,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-上海70岁上访维权人士胡琴珍被软禁（图）/","date":"2012-08-28T23:01:37Z","modified":"2012-08-28T23:01:37Z","title":"维权网 | 上海70岁上访维权人士胡琴珍被软禁（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员晨晓报道）自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>至今，上海市浦东新区周浦镇烈士遗孤、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>多岁高龄的胡琴珍，被周浦镇政府囚禁在家里，多人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时日夜看守在其家门口，不让胡琴珍出门，这样的软禁不知何时才结束。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据称，周浦镇政府怕胡琴珍去北京天安门广场撒发：《上海地方政府腐败渎职偷拆民房无人管》的传单。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年周浦镇政府趁胡琴珍不在家，偷偷将她的的农村宅基地私房拆除，不给她父母的份额。于是，胡琴珍走上依法维权的路。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年遭到拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日的处罚，每当逢年过节或者外国首脑访华，或者中央开重大会议等等，胡琴珍与众多维权者一样都会遭到关押失去人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡琴珍身患糖尿病、高血压、心脏病、脑梗塞等多种疾病，因她无钱医病，支付不起医药费，身体健康状况日益糟糕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡琴珍求助维权网等各界人士关注。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡琴珍电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18721457506</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-mrGYQHwnRy4/UDz2DiGVceI/AAAAAAAAMeE/BTni3ilkoVY/s1600/%E8%83%A1%E7%90%B4%E7%8F%8D%E5%90%91%E4%B8%96%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%86%A4%E6%83%85SCI0304.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-mrGYQHwnRy4/UDz2DiGVceI/AAAAAAAAMeE/BTni3ilkoVY/s320/%E8%83%A1%E7%90%B4%E7%8F%8D%E5%90%91%E4%B8%96%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%86%A4%E6%83%85SCI0304.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JcGKhkbYq8c/UDz2INrcHsI/AAAAAAAAMeM/pGlXyUNwNVo/s1600/%E8%83%A1%E7%90%B4%E7%8F%8D%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+032.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JcGKhkbYq8c/UDz2INrcHsI/AAAAAAAAMeM/pGlXyUNwNVo/s1600/%E8%83%A1%E7%90%B4%E7%8F%8D%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+032.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-rvfj9BHV9cg/UDz2OOYwStI/AAAAAAAAMeU/8LZ1_g8YYhA/s1600/DSCI0310.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-rvfj9BHV9cg/UDz2OOYwStI/AAAAAAAAMeU/8LZ1_g8YYhA/s1600/DSCI0310.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3898656965645753477?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}